### Get departures - Bergen to Stavanger
GET http://localhost:3000/api/departures?from=Bergen&to=Stavanger&date=2026-04-10

### Get departures - Bergen to Hirtshals
GET http://localhost:3000/api/departures?from=Bergen&to=Hirtshals&date=2026-04-10

### Get departures - reverse route
GET http://localhost:3000/api/departures?from=Stavanger&to=Bergen&date=2026-04-10

### Missing params - should return 400 error
GET http://localhost:3000/api/departures?from=Bergen

